{
  "texts": [
    "• Prediction layer: This layer predicts the sentiment quadruples based on the grid-tagging labels.",
    "The model was optimized during training using the cross-entropy loss function, computed based on the predicted sentiment quadruples and the ground truth labels.",
    "The model was trained end-to-end using backpropagation and stochastic gradient descent.",
    "micro F1 and identification F1 were used for measurements, where micro F1 measures the entire quadruples, including sentiment polarity, while identification F1 (Barnes et al. 2021) Xu et al. (2021), which was edited to enumerate triplets and made compatible with DiaASQ.",
    "The fourth model is PARAPHRASE (Zhang et al. 2021a), which outputs were modified to adapt to the DiaASQ task."
  ]
}